dc_description_s: 1 map 36 x 47 cm.|Relief shown pictorially.|Vignette in upper right corner depicts a woman holding a cornucopia of fruits and vegetables and a list of islands in the Loire river in the upper left.|This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1637 and 1680.|From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan.
